These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, indie, folk, dubstep, pop
There are 5 different favourite colors: ivory, chestnut, red, black, grey
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, coffee, juice, water
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, zinnia, rose, iris, bellflower
 1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is the fan of pop##1
 3. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 4. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is the person who likes black##1
 6. the person who likes chestnut is the fan of indie##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 8. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
 9. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
10. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is the person who growsorchid##1
12. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Music-Genre         | indie  | gospel    | dubstep | folk    | pop  |
| Color   | chestnut  | ivory | red | black | grey  |
| Beverage           | almond-milk     | water     | juice  | lemonade   | coffee    |
| Flower         | rose | iris    | zinnia | orchid  | bellflower |

