.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, iced-tea, 7up, cola
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, old-henry, chaman, siglo, pall-mall
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rugby, golf, sailing, skiing, swimming
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, funk, salsa, blues, jazz
 1. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 2. the fan of salsa is the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 9. the fan of blues is the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is the old-henry-smoker##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Beverage          | iced-tea        | cola | almond-milk     | 7up      | mirinda  |
| Cigar           | old-henry   | chaman | pall-mall    | siglo | prince |
| Sport   | sailing | skiing     | swimming | rugby    | golf  |
| Music-Genre   | blues     | funk | rock    | jazz      | salsa    |

