.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, june, december, march, october
5 different games are played: snooker, whist, bridge, go, monopoly
5 different pets are kept: hamster, cat, rabbit, goldfish, rat
There 5 different types of food: apricot, avocado, kiwi, onion, pumpkin
 1. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is in the middle##1
10. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is the person playing snooker##1
12. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
13. the person who's birthday is in march is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Birthday      | march          | december  | june       | january     | october      |
| Game         | whist | monopoly | go  | bridge   | snooker    |
| Pet   | cat        | rat | hamster | goldfish    | rabbit   |
| Food     | apricot   | kiwi | pumpkin      | avocado | onion |

