.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, singing, collecting, magic-tricks, police-officerd-games
There are 5 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, mirinda, almond-milk, sprite
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, american, malaysian, french, italian
The people have 5 different jobs:  security-guard, police-officer, engineer, software-developer, lawyer
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the japanese##1
 2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the american is the person drinking 7up##1
 4. the japanese is the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the french##1
 6. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the police-officer is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the lawyer is in the middle##1
 9. the french is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person who's hobby is police-officerd-games is the malaysian##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is police-officerd-games##1
12. the security-guard is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby          | magic-tricks        | chess       | collecting | singing   | police-officerd-games  |
| Beverage   | sprite | mirinda | 7up | milk   | almond-milk |
| Nationality   | french         | italian     | american | japanese | malaysian     |
| Job     | security-guard        | police-officer        | lawyer    | software-developer    | engineer      |

