.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-5::.
5 different pets are kept: cat, frog, guinea-pig, rat, fish
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, pall-mall-climbing, reading, card-games, fishing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, montecristo, tiparillo, alhambra, pall-mall
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, may, february, august, december
 1. the montecristo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is in the middle##1
 9. the owner of the frog is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
10. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the fish is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
12. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Pet          | frog    | fish  | guinea-pig | cat    | rat      |
| Hobby           | fishing | reading | hiking  | card-games | pall-mall-climbing |
| Cigar   | tiparillo           | montecristo      | pall-mall      | alhambra        | baccarat     |
| Birthday         | may         | february  | january   | august       | december  |

