 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is the person traveling to hannover##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
11. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1
