.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
City: edinburgh, london, hamburg, colone, venice
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, havana, old-henry, dannemann, bongani
The people have 5 different jobs:  firefighter, lawyer, software-developer, doctor, writer
There 5 different types of food: kale, radish, banana, spinach, orange
 1. the havana-smoker is on the left of the writer##1
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
 3. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the firefighter##1
 4. the person eating radish is on the left of the lawyer##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 6. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 7. the havana-smoker is the person eating kale##1
 8. the firefighter is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the person eating orange is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
10. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
11. the person eating spinach is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
12. the old-henry-smoker is the doctor##1
13. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| City      | edinburgh      | london       | venice         | colone  | hamburg |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | dannemann | havana | baccarat  | bongani  |
| Job   | doctor    | lawyer    | firefighter        | writer | software-developer     |
| Food           | radish | banana      | kale       | spinach   | orange   |

