5 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, siglo, davidoff, ritmeester, prince
There 5 different types of food: pear, carrot, radish, grapefruit, tomato
 1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 7. the person who growsaconite is the person eating pear##1
 8. the person who growstulip is the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the siglo-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the fonseca-smoker is the person traveling to hannover##1
11. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
12. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
13. the person who growszinnia is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
