 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is the person traveling to boston##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 7. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is in the middle##1
10. the wooden house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
11. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
12. the person playing billiard is the person traveling to berlin##1
13. the palace house is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

