 6. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 7. the palace house is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
11. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
12. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
13. the person traveling to new-york is the person watching comedy movies##1
14. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1

